        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'You wanted to know more about the Purifying Force, Commandant?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 5,
        "ActionId": 4,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Can you tell me?', 3: '5', 4: 'I wanted to know more about you, actually.', 5: '11'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'As you know, the Purifying Force is the task force that specializes in purifying Constructs.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Although we do fight Corrupted sometimes, our main duty is to hunt down defected Constructs.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: '...Deserters such as Watanabe.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'I\\'m sure they all have their reasons. But in an army, unity is the most important thing.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'If we allow Constructs to desert or abandon their missions, any task force could crumble at any second.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": 18,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'That is why the Purifying Force is established, to prevent that from happening.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'I see... I\\'m sure I\\'ve asked you to treat me as a tool.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'But if your objective is to better implement me on the battlefield... then I\\'ll comply.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'That said, there\\'s not much to know about me. As you\\'re aware, I\\'m Bianca, one of the team captains of the Purifying Force.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 14,
